Scenario 3: Identify Products with Declining Sales

Question
Find products with lower prices compared to expensive products.

Tables Used
products

Logic Explanation
Use the products table.
Compare product prices.
Filter products with lower values.

SQL Query
SELECT product_id, product_name, price
FROM products
WHERE price < 500;

Result:

| product_id | product_name | price |
| ---------- | ------------ | ----- |
| 3          | Tablet       | 300   |
| 4          | Headphones   | 100   |
| 5          | Smartwatch   | 200   |


