Scenario 4: Calculate Moving Average of Sales

Question
Calculate average sales amount.

Tables Used
sales

Logic Explanation
Use the AVG() aggregate function.
Calculate average sales from the sales table.

SQL Query
SELECT AVG(amount) AS average_sales
FROM sales;

Result:

| average_sales |
| ------------- |
| 5200          |

